RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.Type AS 'Type', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.Status AS 'Status', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.PeerStatus AS 'Peer Status' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, Port, DcbxLogicalLinkResult, LldpNodeConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LldpNodeConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND DcbxLogicalLinkResult.ParentHnd = LldpNodeConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND DcbxLogicalLinkResult.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LldpNodeConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.Type AS 'Type', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.Status AS 'Status', DcbxLogicalLinkResult.PeerStatus AS 'Peer Status' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, ExternalDevicePort, DcbxLogicalLinkResult, Port, LldpNodeConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LldpNodeConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND DcbxLogicalLinkResult.ParentHnd = LldpNodeConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND DcbxLogicalLinkResult.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LldpNodeConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
